data.description: Imagine living in this adorable northeast-facing townhome with its great location JUST a few short MINUTES to GA400, the Halcyon and BB's Bagels (yum!).  You'll MOVE RIGHT IN and start enjoying your prestigious ALPHARETTA ADDRESS with LOWER FORSYTH COUNTY PROPERTY TAXES.  Here's what else we know YOU'LL LOVE...Your retreat from the world is your OVERSIZED owner's suite with separate sitting room and 2 LARGE WALK-IN CLOSETS. Your private, MAINTENANCE-FREE BACKYARD.CONVENIENT GUEST PARKING right down the street, and NO MORE YARD WORK!  Featuring FRESH INTERIOR PAINT in the latest designer color (exterior is taken care of for you by the HOA!), newly installed CARPETING, new tile in upstairs bathrooms, plus a BRAND-NEW HVAC. You'll also enjoy the laundry on the second floor and the SUPER CUTE AND DESIRABLE BALCONY where you can soon spend warm evenings sipping a cool beverage.  No rent restrictions here.  Hurry, this well-priced townhome won't last long!
